==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Twilly
<hw>Twil"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Willy</er>.]</ety> <def>A machine for cleansing or loosening wool by
the action of a revolving cylinder covered with long iron spikes or
teeth; a willy or willying machine; -- called also <altname>twilly
devil</altname>, and <altname>devil</altname>. See <er>Devil</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>, 6, and <er>Willy</er>.</def>
<rj><au>Tomlinson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Twilt</ent>⟦br⟧
